data.description: This cozy 4 bed 2 bath brick home, with 2 car garage and 3 walk in closets, open floor plan and high ceilings-  is located in a peaceful, family-friendly suburb. You will feel right at home in this neighborly community, where I-37 is comfortably close and within walking distance of Tuloso Midway Intermediate school. This close knit neighborhood is adorned with gorgeous manicured lawns and friendly smiles. You will feel right at home here with a mix of serenity and fun with plenty of dining options nearby and shopping
